				<td colspan="2"><span>After HA5, wouldn't getting Ambi help increase the chances of your epic proc'n in you offhand?  The way I understand it is say (with HA5 even) your main hand triggers dual wield check 100 times, and of those 100 times, you proc DotB 10 times.  With Ambi, you main hand now has a chance trigger dual wield 200 times for example in that same period, which in turn procs DotB 20 times.  Hence more chances at off-hand proc in a given frame of time.  I try to be grouped with melee dps as much as I can on raids, so for me, the longer I can keep the DotB effect up on my group, the better.
<br />

<br />
<i>Ambi increases your chance at dual wield.</i></span></td>
